          <avActivityHighlights>Low avalanche danger will prevail.</avActivityHighlights>
          <avActivityComment>From origins in starting zones where no previous releases have taken place only isolated wet avalanches are possible. Caution is to be exercised on extremely steep shady slopes. Mostly avalanches are rather small.</avActivityComment>
